 Rodríguez Toro), gramática (por Roberto Cuadros Muñoz) y léxico (por Cristóbal José Álvarez López). Se ha añadido al final un completo índice onomástico que recoge los nombres de todas las personas citadas en el corpus.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aCuadros Muñoz, Roberto, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2024z9783111332369oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869545740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968695457423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968695457/original  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-207-IBVb2024